James Cossins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Cossins 0 James Cossins (4 December 1933 – 12 February 1997) was an English character actor. Born in Beckenham, Kent, he became widely recognised as the abrupt, bewildered Mr Walt in the Fawlty Towers episode "The Hotel Inspectors" and as Mr Watson the frustrated Public Relations training course instructor in an episode of Some Mothers Do 'Ave 'Em.
